{"type": "article", "id": 15489, "title": "超简约单身公寓是这样的：工作、吃饭、睡觉全在一个橱柜里", "description": "餐桌、床、书柜、电脑桌，全部集中在了一个集装箱式的盒子里。", "date": "2015-09-24T13:55:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 16584, "name": "公寓设计"}, {"id": 16585, "name": "空间节省"}, {"id": 734, "name": "集装箱"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 331, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121336XDMWkeBOldtfmoHE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个位于纽约的单身公寓，<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/23/a-custom-space-saving-solution-designed-for-a-small-new-york-apartment/\" target=\"_blank\">把空间节省做到了极致</a>。书架、电脑、餐桌竟然全部融合在一个蓝色的柜子里，打开柜门，里面竟然还隐藏着睡觉用的床……\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121330AidkSEt25ngLO8rx.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"694\" title=\"这是那个纽约公寓的空间\" alt=\"这是那个纽约公寓的空间\" data-ratio=\"1.084375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>这是那个纽约公寓的空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121331JbdBG38lTgyj5Cop.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" title=\"这就是所有的面积了\" alt=\"这就是所有的面积了\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>这就是所有的面积了</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121331v34ThzMoxcaSUq2O.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" title=\"蓝色“集装箱”上的电脑桌可以放下来\" alt=\"蓝色“集装箱”上的电脑桌可以放下来\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>蓝色“集装箱”上的电脑桌可以收起来</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031213325W9e3w1VSAizp27k.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" title=\"打开集装箱门\" alt=\"打开集装箱门\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>打开集装箱门</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121332fiUCbPS6H4ljsEz8.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"476\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.74375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121333KElMx5k2mXiSRjLB.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" title=\"正面\" alt=\"正面\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>正面</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121333crWeJdoi6Y7UVTpX.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" title=\"床隐藏在这里\" alt=\"床隐藏在这里\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>床隐藏在这里</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121334Th0j9OGd8CJcv7KY.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" title=\"将床放下来\" alt=\"将床放下来\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>将床放下来</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121334X7RL8OBwIpe63uzx.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t床头甚至还有一个书架\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031213344qJCPlURIazwjFTf.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" title=\"餐桌\" alt=\"餐桌\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>餐桌</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这个狭小的空间是<a href=\"http://mkca.com\" target=\"_blank\">建筑事务所 MICHAEL K CHEN ARCHITECTURE </a>设计完成的，虽然节省了空间，但不知道多次拖动后，家具的质量如何？\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t除了家具设计，他们还完成了许多其他作品：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121335CpVeU5nfHALDQbui.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"421\" title=\"UPPER EAST SIDE TOWNHOUSE\" alt=\"UPPER EAST SIDE TOWNHOUSE\" data-ratio=\"0.6578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>UPPER EAST SIDE TOWNHOUSE</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031213351gu5vtESkUa9s7FN.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" title=\"K-G DESK AND STORAGE SYSTEM\" alt=\"K-G DESK AND STORAGE SYSTEM\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>K-G DESK AND STORAGE SYSTEM</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121336BTLwOX4IYiD2nZcE.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"400\" title=\"AERATED APARTMENT\" alt=\"AERATED APARTMENT\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>AERATED APARTMENT</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/23/a-custom-space-saving-solution-designed-for-a-small-new-york-apartment/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>contemporist</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}